# POAP claim/mint links — anyone with these URLs can claim a POAP.
# Public-repo backstop: never commit them. Primary storage is
# apps/backend/data/pizza_day_poap_codes.txt (already gitignored), but
# entries here defend against accidental commits if a list ever lands
# at the repo root or under a *_poap_*.txt name.
poaps.txt
*_poap_codes*.txt
*_poaps*.txt

